x4freetext: Ratio of experimental Cm-245 spectrum to Maxwellian
distribution of T=1.385 MeV is given on Fig.5.
Data 1, 2 at 2.97 MeV looks like suspicious - too low.
on fig.5 there is no strong deviation of these exp.data
from Maxwellian shape about at 3.MeV point.
So this data line was deleted:
MEV   NO-DIM  NO-DIM  ARB-UNITS  ARB-UNITS  ARB-UNITS
